From: "Mark Ackerman" <mackerman@novell.com>
To: <duwe@suse.de>
Subject: kernel-SLRS
Patch-mainline: never
References: SUSE47705

Kernel hook for POS AT-kbd filter, to be used for kernel-SLRS exclusively.
Customers who buy http://www.pc.ibm.com/store/products/software/ires/ will
receive that including kernels with this hook enabled. All others will most
likely not be interested in this.

Signed-off-by: duwe@suse.de
Signed-off-by: vojtech@suse.cz

